17:18.507 --> 17:20.599
Strainer. That's brilliant.

17:20.809 --> 17:22.106
Sunny, how's that pot coming?

17:25.747 --> 17:30.650
Sunny, that's not a pot.
It's a spittoon.

17:30.919 --> 17:33.410
A spittoon? You mean, like. . .?

17:35.224 --> 17:36.316
We'll wash it twice.

17:39.628 --> 17:40.720
Well?

17:41.029 --> 17:42.929
It's good. It's really good.

17:43.131 --> 17:44.098
Time check.

17:44.733 --> 17:47.429
Let's go back to prehistoric times,

17:47.736 --> 17:50.933
when dinosaurs ruled the earth.

18:04.686 --> 18:07.177
Baudelaire orphans
