to the courtesy desk.

18:21.937 --> 18:22.995
What do you want?

18:23.639 --> 18:25.504
Dinner is served.

18:28.944 --> 18:30.036
Puttanesca.

18:30.412 --> 18:31.743
What did you call me?

18:32.247 --> 18:35.410
It's pasta. Pasta puttanesca.

18:35.651 --> 18:37.346
Where's the roast beef?

18:38.120 --> 18:39.610
Roast beef?

18:40.122 --> 18:41.749
Beef. Yes. Roast beef.

18:42.624 --> 18:45.923
It's the Swedish term for beef
that is roasted.

18:47.462 --> 18:50.158
But you didn't tell us
you wanted roast beef.

18:54.636 --> 18:59.403
You know, there's a big world out there
filled with desperate orphans

18:59.608 --> 19:02.168
who would gladly swim across
an ocean of thumbtacks

19:02.377 --> 19:07.576
just to be eclipsed by the long shadow
that is cast by my accomplishments.

19:08.083 --> 19:10.074
But I don't care about them.

19:10.686 --> 19:13.382
I chose to open my heart

19:13.822 --> 19:17.121
to you two loverly children

19:17.492 --> 19:19.585
and your hideous primate.

19:19.795 --> 19:23.231
All I ask in return is that you do each
and every thing that pops into my head

19:23.432 --> 19:27.596
while I enjoy the enormous fortune
your parents left behind.

19:28.036 --> 19:30.436
- No.
- Why, you litt--

19:45.921 --> 19:50.017
It's time you children learned
a little respect.

19:50.258 --> 19:51.350
You put her down!

19:54.129 --> 19:55.721
You monster!

19:59.067 --> 20:01.331
You all saw it. The boy slipped.

20:01.536 --> 20:04.027
You won't get a cent
until Violet turns 18.

20:04.673 --> 20:06.470
Oh, really?

20:07.042 --> 20:07.974
Says who?

20:08.243 --> 20:09.733
The law. Look it up.

20:09.945 --> 20:12.345
We're going to call Mr. Poe
about this right now.

20:20.455 --> 20:21.752
Are you?

20:24.559 --> 20:27.187
I'm very disappointed
in you, children.

20:30.365 --> 20:32.299
Where were we?

20:33.001 --> 20:34.366
Are you okay?

20:34.569 --> 20:36.059
No.

20:39.775 --> 20:41.072
Klaus, what are you doing?

20:41.309 --> 20:43.300
- I'm going.
- Going where?

20:43.512 --> 20:44.774
Home.

20:45.313 --> 20:47.372
This is our home now.

20:49.785 --> 20:51.480
This is not home.

20:51.987 --> 20:54.581
Home is where your parents
put you to bed at night.

20:54.890 --> 20:56.323
Where they teach you to ride a bike.

20:56.625 --> 20:59.719
Or where they get all choked up
on your first day of school.

20:59.928 --> 21:02.260
This is not home.

21:06.034 --> 21:07.865
How could they do this to us?

21:08.070 --> 21:09.230
They're just bad people.

21:09.771 --> 21:11.830
Not them. Mom and Dad.

21:12.040 --> 21:13.632
- Klaus!
- What?

21:13.842 --> 21:16.868
Violet, you're thinking it too.
How could they?

21:17.145 --> 21:18.772
They had no plan for us at all?

21:19.047 --> 21:21.140
Well, maybe they did have a plan.

21:21.950 --> 21:23.941
Well, sure looks like it to me.

21:31.793 --> 21:34.853
Do you remember
when Mom and Dad went to Europe?

21:35.864 --> 21:39.061
And we thought they'd abandoned us
because they didn't even write.

21:39.267 --> 21:40.962
Then we found out they'd written
a long letter.

21:41.169 --> 21:42.466
It had just gotten lost in the mail.

21:42.671 --> 21:46.163
Do you remember how guilty we felt
for thinking bad thoughts about them?

21:47.709 --> 21:48.869
This is just like that.

21:50.078 --> 21:51.477
No, it's not.

21:52.380 --> 21:53.608
Why?

21:55.917 --> 21:59.819
Because they're not in Europe.
They're not coming back.

22:07.028 --> 22:11.158
Do you think anything
will ever feel like home again?

22:24.746 --> 22:26.236
''Sanctuary''

22:26.548 --> 22:31.850
is a word which here means, ''a small,
safe place in a troubling world. ''

22:33.054 --> 22:38.048
Like an oasis in a vast desert
or an island in a stormy sea.

22:38.360 --> 22:41.090
The Baudelaires enjoyed their evening
in the sanctuary they'd built together.

22:41.296 --> 22:42.263
I see it. I see it.

22:42.464 --> 22:46.867
But in their hearts they knew that
the troubling world lay just outside.

22:47.068 --> 22:50.902
A world which, I'm sad to say,
can be described in two dismal words.

22:51.206 --> 22:53.071
Custody granted.

22:55.911 --> 22:59.506
Thank you, Your Honor.
Nice doing business with you.

